                  "description": "An unforgettable disco experience with stunning sea views\n\nGet on board and enjoy a disco party at the Helsinki sea! The legendary disco cruises, organized in cooperation with Helmiradio, will take you out to the sea to enjoy the breath-taking views and unique atmosphere.\n\nM/S Emma departures are full of disco beats from the ’70s until today. Onboard the party is kept going by the DJ.\n\nCruises every Friday 6.5.-7.10.2022 at: 18:00-22:00"
