              "en": {
                  "name": "Finnish Smoke Sauna Experience",
                  "description": "Experience an authentic smoke sauna and swim in a freshwater lake. During this guided sauna experience, you will learn about the culture around the sauna and enjoy all the benefits of it while doing so. The sauna is heated between 80-100°C and water is thrown on the rocks which sends a wave of heat into the room. \n\nAfter some time in the sauna, you will step outside for fresh air and a cooling dip in the lake year-round. Sit, Sweat, Swim, Repeat! You will remember this experience for the rest of your life!\n\nHighlights:\n• Enjoy an authentic Finnish smoke sauna\n• Swim in a freshwater lake\n• Extremely relaxing and laidback experience\n• Do the most Finnish thing possible"
              },
              "fi": {
                  "name": "Koe autenttinen savusauna",
                  "description": "Lähde Taiga Timesin kanssa Kuusijärvelle ja koe autenttinen savusauna!\n\nOletko koskaan käynyt savusaunassa? Tai oletko koskaan uinut avannossa? \nNyt olisi mahdollisuus kokeilla molemmat! Savusauna tarjoaa parhaimmat ja lämpöisimmät löylyt, ja tauon aikana voit pulahtaa järveen oli sitten kesä tai talvi.\n\nTähän saunapakettiin kuuluu kuljetus, opas, pyyhkeet, saunasandaalit ja sisäänpääsymaksu. \n"
              }
