              "en": {
                  "name": "Winter Archipelago Excursion",
                  "description": "Join Taiga Times to experience a unique side of Finland, the quiet nature side and visit one of the world’s largest archipelago. A walk in this nature reserve highlights why Finland is one of the best outdoor destinations year-round and why Finns enjoy their peace and quiet. \n\nHighlights:\n • Lookout points of breathtaking archipelago scenery\n • Amazing photographing opportunities\n • Easy walk designed for all levels of fitness\n • Campfire lunch and coffee/tea with a seaside view\n\nA walk into the forest brings on a nature trail with countless smaller trails made by deer, foxes, moose and more! Enjoy the magical winter forest and frozen sea while your guide lights a fire for lunch."
              },
              "fi": {
                  "name": "Talvinen retki Porkkalanniemeen",
                  "description": "Lähde talviseikkailulle Taiga Timesin kanssa ja koe talvinen saaristomaisema! \n\nPorkkalanniemi on tunnettu kesäkohde, mutta myös upea talvinen retkikohde. Tällä retkellä opas johdattaa sinut talvisen metsän läpi upeisiin saaristomaisemiin. Lämmittele nuotion ääressä ja herkuttele lämpimällä välipalalla."
              }
