              "fi": {
                  "name": "Nauti ilta-auringosta Porkkalanniemessä",
                  "description": "Lähde tälle rentouttavalle iltaretkelle Porkkalanniemeen ja nauti ilta-auringon säteistä saaristomaisemissa. Tällä opastetulla retkellä kuljetaan saaristometsän läpi luontopolkua pitkin ja nautitaan eväät kalliolla nauttien ilta-auringon värjäämästä horisontista."
              },
              "en": {
                  "name": "Midnight Sun in the Archipelago",
                  "description": "Imagine a summer night that never ends; while your family is at home sleeping, you are out walking under the midnight sun. This wonderful display is a stark contrast that affects all walks of life in Finland and while the season is short; Taiga Times makes the most of it. \n\nHighlights:\n • Experience the midnight sun in a remote setting \n • Evening walks offer a new perspective to the forest\n • Calm and peaceful environment \n • Evening snack with seaside view\n\nTaiga Times gives you an authentic nature experience in one of the most beautiful coastal areas of Finland. This evening trip starts from Helsinki and it will take you to Porkkalanniemi, a peninsula that reaches out into the midst of the world's largest archipelago."
              }
