          "descriptions": {
              "en": {
                  "name": "Fly, Dine & Sail",
                  "description": "Fly above Helsinki, land on an island, dine and sail back to the city center!\n-Not forgetting the celebration of authentic delicacies made from season's purest ingredients!\n\nExperience Helsinki and it's surrounding archipelago on a 25 minute scenic helicopter flight while having a glass of Champagne. Land on the bear cliffs of a typical Finnish island in the outer skirts of Helsinki Archipelago. Enjoy an unforgettable dinner made by a local top chef and sail back to the city center while watching the sunset on a spacious catamaran sailboat with a professional crew onboard.\n​\nThis experience is always customised according to your taste, needs and the season. If you wish to do so, during the summer time you get to pick up wild herbs, berries or mushrooms on the island with your chef who is more than happy to show you how to turn them into delicacies you get to enjoy on the boat later on. The experience can also be organised during the winter time with activities such as ice fishing or survival suit floating. During the winter, the return to the city is organised with a helicopter and dining is organised on the Island."
              },
              "fi": {
                  "name": "Fly, Dine & Sail - nauti luonnosta helikopterilennolla, saaristossa ja merellä ruokaa unohtamatta!",
                  "description": "Lennä Helsingin yläpuolella, laskeudu saarelle ja purjehdi takaisin kaupunkiin! Nauti kauden puhtaimmista raaka-aineista valmistettujen aitojen herkkujen juhlaa!\n\nKoe Helsinki ja sen ympäröivä saaristo 25 minuutin upealla helikopterilennolla samalla kun nautit lasillisen kuplivaa. Laskeudu saaristoon ja nauti huippukokin tekemästä illallisesta ja purjehdi takaisin keskustaan ​​katsellen auringonlaskua tilavalla katamaraanipurjeveneellä, jonka aluksella on ammattitaitoinen miehistö.\n\n"
              }
          },
